	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You tap into a creature's nightmares, drawing one of their worst fears into an illusion only they can see. Your magic makes it appear that your illusion is in the process of killing your target, and your target is overwhelmed with pain.</em></p><p><strong>Wisdom Save</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> The target takes [[/damage 6d10 psychic]] damage* and becomes &amp;reference[Frightened]. While frightened in this way, the target's speed is 0. Target rolls again at end of their turns, ending effect on success.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage, no other effect.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> Increase damage by [[/damage 1d10 psychic]]{1d10} for each spell level above 4th.</p>",
			"chat": ""
		},
